My usual type?

00:00:31.164 --> 00:00:33.199
Oh, in a good way.

00:00:34.434 --> 00:00:36.436
He's not what I imagined.

00:00:37.437 --> 00:00:42.709
How do I put this?
Mitsuhiro is a really nice guy.

00:00:44.010 --> 00:00:45.011
Really?

00:00:46.112 --> 00:00:47.113
Yes.

00:00:47.547 --> 00:00:48.915
He's perfect for you.

00:00:51.418 --> 00:00:52.419
Thank you.

00:00:52.752 --> 00:00:55.188
No, I'm glad he's a good guy.

00:00:55.321 --> 00:00:57.624
She always compared herself to me

00:00:58.358 --> 00:01:00.260
as if it were a contest.

00:01:00.527 --> 00:01:01.528
Hey, Mitsuhiro.

00:01:01.828 --> 00:01:04.264
Yurika used to work
at a general trading company.

00:01:04.330 --> 00:01:05.432
Goodness!

00:01:05.665 --> 00:01:07.300
You must be so smart.

00:01:07.400 --> 00:01:08.501
No, not at all.

00:01:08.668 --> 00:01:11.671
