00:01:23.383 --> 00:01:25.018
I could never do it.

00:01:25.885 --> 00:01:26.886
No way.

00:01:27.554 --> 00:01:28.922
You're incredible.

00:01:30.090 --> 00:01:33.126
Well, I don't think
I could stop working for a while.

00:01:35.061 --> 00:01:36.729
- Good luck.
- Yes.

00:01:36.996 --> 00:01:41.034
Did that actually provoke
Yurika even more?

00:02:29.949 --> 00:02:31.317
I don't want to believe it.

00:02:36.256 --> 00:02:38.124
ODEN SHOP MARUTA

00:02:39.092 --> 00:02:44.697
ODEN SHOP MARUTA

00:02:47.700 --> 00:02:49.569
Your husband was at this oden shop?

00:02:50.703 --> 00:02:51.704
Yes.

00:02:52.906 --> 00:02:53.907
I see.

00:02:55.108 --> 00:02:57.210
We'll look into this as well.

00:02:57.477 --> 00:02:58.478
Well...

00:03:08.454 --> 00:03:11.491
He might've been with her.

00:03:12.692 --> 00:03:13.693
Who is this?

