Are you sure you want us to check?

00:03:36.416 --> 00:03:38.251
I'm too scared to ask her myself.

00:03:43.556 --> 00:03:44.557
Ma'am.

00:03:45.925 --> 00:03:46.926
Yes?

00:03:49.529 --> 00:03:52.765
Do you really want him to come back?

00:04:00.206 --> 00:04:01.207
Yes.

00:05:22.689 --> 00:05:25.725
PLEASE DIE MY BELOVED

00:05:34.100 --> 00:05:35.868
I'll pay the oden shop a visit.

00:05:36.069 --> 00:05:38.004
Yes, thank you.

00:05:44.711 --> 00:05:47.680
Must be tough knowing your husband
cheated with your friend.

00:05:48.448 --> 00:05:50.416
Keep tabs on Yurika Sakaki for now.

00:05:51.384 --> 00:05:52.385
Yes, sir.

00:06:05.765 --> 00:06:06.966
Have a good day.

00:06:08.534 --> 00:06:09.969
I'll come home early.

00:06:11.170 --> 00:06:12.171
I see.

00:06:13.806 --> 00:06:15.541
Want to drink more?

00:06:27.553 --> 00:06:28.721
Get ready.

00:06:37.930 --> 00:06:39.165
So gross!

00:06:39.232 --> 00:06:43.403
Hurry up and die!

00:06:51.310 --> 00:06:52.311
Riko.

00:06:52.545 --> 00:06:54.847
I made you lunch, so have some later.

00:06:59.919 --> 00:07:03.856
And I did some meal prep,
so eat this, too.

00:07:08.928 --> 00:07:10.363
I went to the doctor's.

00:07:10.963 --> 00:07:12.465
They said the baby is healthy.

00:07:13.866 --> 00:07:15.568
It's finally starting to feel real.

00:07:17.236 --> 00:07:18.237
I'm fine with just us.

00:07:20.606 --> 00:07:21.607
What?

00:07:22.041 --> 00:07:24.744
I like it
when it's just the two of us.

00:07:27.747 --> 00:07:28.748
So...

00:07:31.250 --> 00:07:32.485
let's get an abortion.

00:07:38.191 --> 00:07:39.192
Ryosuke?

00:07:42.094 --> 00:07:43.496
You're not serious, right?

00:07:48.234 --> 00:07:50.870
I love you, Riko.

00:07:52.038 --> 00:07:53.806
I want to live with you,
the two of us.

00:07:55.575 --> 00:07:56.909
Don't you?

00:08:21.901 --> 00:08:23.135
Here.

