Hello, I look forward
to working with you again.

00:10:37.937 --> 00:10:39.372
I can't believe her.

00:10:40.539 --> 00:10:42.508
This will be hard on Kana, too.

00:10:42.942 --> 00:10:44.243
Well, let's see how this goes.

00:10:48.681 --> 00:10:51.417
Hello, I'll be in your care.

00:11:07.466 --> 00:11:09.502
- I look forward to working with you.
- Me, too.

00:11:17.510 --> 00:11:18.511
YURIKA

00:11:18.577 --> 00:11:20.513
Can we push the date up?
I can't take this anymore.

00:11:20.579 --> 00:11:21.714
Let's meet up. Please respond.

00:11:56.048 --> 00:11:58.584
Now all I need is...

00:12:07.993 --> 00:12:10.429
MAYA

00:12:10.496 --> 00:12:13.632
I'm sorry,
I can't get involved anymore.

00:12:54.540 --> 00:12:56.776
Yes, how are things over there?

00:12:57.710 --> 00:12:59.445
She just left the hardware store.

00:13:01.280 --> 00:13:03.482
But she's not doing
anything particularly shady.

00:13:04.750 --> 00:13:05.751
I see.

00:13:16.061 --> 00:13:17.863
Okay, keep up the good work.

00:13:29.041 --> 00:13:30.309
I missed you, Riko.

00:13:33.112 --> 00:13:34.113
Let's go.

00:13:39.618 --> 00:13:40.619
Riko?

00:13:42.288 --> 00:13:43.322
I...

00:13:49.962 --> 00:13:50.963
want to keep it.

00:13:52.164 --> 00:13:53.165
What?

00:13:55.601 --> 00:13:57.436
I can't abort it.

00:14:02.675 --> 00:14:05.611
Riko, think long and hard about this.

00:14:07.279 --> 00:14:08.981
It doesn't end after giving birth.

00:14:10.816 --> 00:14:11.851
I know.

00:14:14.653 --> 00:14:17.189
Your way of life will change.

00:14:20.292 --> 00:14:21.627
You're choosing the baby

00:14:22.261 --> 00:14:23.429
over spending time with me?

00:14:45.684 --> 00:14:46.685
Excuse me.

00:14:47.553 --> 00:14:48.554
Yes?

00:14:48.621 --> 00:14:50.689
I'm sorry, where's the train station?

00:14:51.824 --> 00:14:52.825
Not sure.

00:15:03.802 --> 00:15:05.337
He smells like medicine?

00:15:25.925 --> 00:15:28.694
Hello, thank you for the other day.

00:15:28.928 --> 00:15:31.163
Please don't talk to me here.

00:15:31.530 --> 00:15:33.098
- But--
- Goodbye.

00:15:38.637 --> 00:15:40.806
- Do you have a moment?
- Yes.

00:15:40.873 --> 00:15:42.608
I'm with the police.

00:15:43.943 --> 00:15:44.977
I see.

00:15:45.077 --> 00:15:47.279
How do you know that lady?

00:15:48.747 --> 00:15:49.915
I don't really know her.

00:15:50.616 --> 00:15:52.251
She called out to me on the street.

00:15:52.918 --> 00:15:55.754
I think it was last Saturday.

00:15:55.821 --> 00:15:56.855
Last Saturday?

00:15:56.922 --> 00:15:57.923
Yes.

00:15:57.990 --> 00:15:58.991
Please take one.

00:16:09.535 --> 00:16:10.569
Please take one.

00:16:11.236 --> 00:16:12.404
Thank you.

00:16:20.045 --> 00:16:21.146
Excuse me.

00:16:23.382 --> 00:16:24.383
Take some.

00:16:25.884 --> 00:16:28.454
Do you have time after this?

00:16:29.088 --> 00:16:30.089
What?

00:16:30.456 --> 00:16:33.792
She said she'd give me 10,000 yen
if I posed for some photos.

00:16:34.259 --> 00:16:36.595
I just needed to show
bits of myself, like my hands.

00:16:44.136 --> 00:16:45.137
All right.

00:16:46.638 --> 00:16:50.109
TODAY'S DATE WITH MY HUSBAND

00:16:50.175 --> 00:16:51.343
#LUNCHDATE #MOTHER

