I even changed clothes for her

00:17:23.275 --> 00:17:25.210
but even just greeting her
made her snap at me.

00:17:28.113 --> 00:17:29.248
Are we done here?

00:17:32.217 --> 00:17:34.086
Here's the photo.

00:17:34.353 --> 00:17:36.522
