And she's gotten involved
with a medical professional.

00:17:51.770 --> 00:17:53.772
This is so messy.

00:17:54.273 --> 00:17:56.375
Looks like
we should take this seriously.

00:17:56.809 --> 00:17:59.011
- You should always do that.
- Right.

00:17:59.144 --> 00:18:01.346
TODAY'S DATE WITH MY HUSBAND
#LUNCHDATE #MOTHER

00:18:01.413 --> 00:18:03.549
SO WONDERFUL!
