It wasn't always like this.

00:22:26.011 --> 00:22:27.012
I'm sorry.

00:22:28.580 --> 00:22:29.648
It's not your fault.

00:22:31.149 --> 00:22:32.184
It's me.

00:22:33.385 --> 00:22:34.653
It's my body.

00:22:37.456 --> 00:22:38.457
Ever since that day.

00:22:41.026 --> 00:22:43.295
That's the day you stopped smiling.

00:22:45.497 --> 00:22:49.167
The test results say
the problem is on the husband's side.

00:22:52.137 --> 00:22:54.606
Unfortunately, a child is...

